FeatureName: Accessibility Color Description Label

Description:
    Displays a text label describing the current color selected out of the 12
    colors in the main color palette. This label updates whenever a user chooses
    a new color from the palette, providing responsive feedback to users with
    color vision deficiencies or impairments.

Reference:
    US4.004
