FeatureName: New Function (Clear Canvas)

Description:
    The “New” feature resets the canvas instantly, clearing all shapes and
    restoring the default white background so users can begin a new drawing
    without manually undoing multiple actions. When clicked, the button triggers
    a CompositeCommand that removes all existing shapes from the model and
    reinitializes the background color to white.

Reference:
